latestPosts.caption:
It goes deeper than chai ☕️🎀✨

@indewild is healing a generation of South Asian girlies like me who grew up with a lack of representation in the beauty world and could only dream of seeing products like ‘Glazed Jalebi’ and ‘Masala Chai’ Dewy Lip Treatments proudly sitting in @sephorauk 🥹👏🏽

I had the most gorgeous time with the most gorgeous company decorating bento cakes lead by the stunning @cakeshakuk and celebrating Inde Wild’s latest launches 🩷

Thank you for having me! 🫶🏽 *pr invite

latestPosts.caption:
I can’t get enough of this @merit lip combo! 🤎

It’s so comfortable and long-lasting which makes for a perfect everyday lip 👏🏽 And look at that shinee ✨

Products used: 

~ Signature Lip Liner in ‘Sportif’ - a warm peach brown

These new liners glide like butter 🧈 and I love how they’re sheer and soft yet buildable for definition. 

~ Shade Slick tinted lip oil in ‘Tabby’ - a rose brown 

The most beautiful, non-sticky formula! These feel so lovely and nourishing on the lips. 

Have you tried these yet?
